                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18221204-68-off368 t18221204-68-cd369"></join>, a handkerchief, value 2 s. 6 d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18221204-68-victim589" type="victimName">
                           Abraham 
                           Van Over
                        <interp inst="t18221204-68-victim589" type="surname" value="Van Over"></interp>
